title: What is the Graduate+ Award
description: Graduate+ is an extra & co-curricular awards framework offered to all students at BCU across all faculties & courses, it’s designed to help you stand out from the crowd, whilst preparing you for your future.

We do things differently here, when you immerse yourself in everything we have to offer, you’ll be building on your current skillset, whilst having some fun too. You’ll have the chance to consider new ideas, network with others, attend events, and work on projects – all of which will help you to grow both professionally and personally for your future, and beyond.
This is an amazing opportunity for you to develop and test your skills and graduate capabilities while getting you to step outside your comfort zone.

title: Discover Your Digital Skills
description: First, reserve the spot and refresh the page, then you will see the option to join the meeting in Teams.
Please NOTE: Use your BCU Student Email to attend the session.
We recommend joining the session 2-3 minutes prior to the scheduled start time, to ensure you do not miss any information.
Use the link provided to join the session.
If you have any issues, please contact us at graduateplus@bcu.ac.uk.
